577
00:29:32,786 --> 00:29:33,756
and export compliance.


578
00:29:33,756 --> 00:29:35,896
We have added a new
tab under Features.


579
00:29:36,436 --> 00:29:40,766
Today, when you submit your
app, whether it's for beta


580
00:29:40,766 --> 00:29:42,126
or for the App Store, we ask,


