users, as well as have access


657
00:33:47,206 --> 00:33:50,086
to create in-app purchases,
leaderboards, achievements,


658
00:33:50,436 --> 00:33:52,116
and view Resolution Center.


659
00:33:53,796 --> 00:33:55,396
And these are the changes
that we are rolling


660
00:33:55,396 --> 00:33:58,016
